{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs32 A1 Data\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 We are using mobile subscription data from A1. A1 is the largest network operator in Austria with 5.3 million subscribers. The used data was recorded on the network of A1 between Monday, November 2010 and Sunday, November 2010. The captured interfaces, events and the data structure of the system will be depicted in the succeeding subsections.\par}
